description:
The story of David and his soldiers fighting for and saving their families represents how God is going to save us from the devil.

"The Shepherd King" is a 12-part revival series with Pastor @PastorBatchelor first aired in Spring of 2017. Few Old Testament characters have had as much impact on the modern Christian faith as David, the beloved shepherd-king of Israel. And today, his story—the challenges, the adventures, and the highs and lows—still has amazing power to inform and transform our walk with God.
